description: Send-AI sends a user prompt to the OpenAI chat completion API (or compatible endpoint) and returns the assistant's response. It supports streaming output to the console or returning the complete response as an object. The API endpoint and key can be configured via environment variables or overridden using the -ApiEndpoint and -ApiKey parameters.
